long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
🚀 Effortlessly extract Upwork jobs data from the list search page to a Excel/CSV/JSON/HTML/XML file.

🔧 How it Works:
1️⃣ Go to the Upwork Jobs Search Page.
2️⃣ Perform a search, then click the "Start" button on extension popup.
3️⃣ Choose to download from the data scraping pop-up or the task list on extension.

✨ Why use this:
👩‍🔬 Product Research Ideas: Understand what services are in demand and how much clients are willing to pay, helping you brainstorm and validate new freelance service offerings.
🦠 Market Analysis: Aggregate and analyze job data to gauge market trends, demand for specific skills, and typical project budgets, providing valuable insights for strategic planning.
🥸 Find Skilled Professionals: Easily locate freelancers who meet the specific requirements of your projects.
📚 Efficient Recruitment: Reduce the time and effort spent on finding the right talent.

Note: This extension is an independent creation and is not affiliated with or endorsed by Upwork❗️🔒
